sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Validating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Operator as OGX Operator<br/>(controller-runtime)
    participant Kustomize as Kustomize Engine<br/>(in-process)
    participant OGXPod as OGX Server Pod<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Ingress as Ingress Controller<br/>80/443 TCP
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Providers as AI Provider Backends<br/>(vLLM, OpenAI, Azure, etc.)

    Note over User, Operator: Flow 1: OGXServer Reconciliation
    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply OGXServer CR
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Admission Review (POST)<br/>TLS (service-serving-cert)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Allowed (validates distribution,<br/>provider IDs, references)
    K8sAPI-->>User: CR created
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event (OGXServer)<br/>ServiceAccount token auth
    Operator->>Kustomize: Render manifests<br/>(name prefix, namespace,<br/>field mutations, NetworkPolicy)
    Kustomize-->>Operator: Rendered resources
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update resources<br/>(Deployment, Service, PVC,<br/>NetworkPolicy, HPA, PDB, SA)
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Resources created
    Operator->>OGXPod: GET /v1/health<br/>HTTP (configurable TLS)
    OGXPod-->>Operator: Health status
    Operator->>OGXPod: GET /v1/providers<br/>GET /v1/version
    OGXPod-->>Operator: Provider info, version
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Update OGXServer status

    Note over Client, OGXPod: Flow 2: External Client Access
    Client->>Ingress: HTTP/HTTPS request<br/>(depends on Ingress controller)
    Ingress->>OGXPod: Forward to {instance}-service<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    OGXPod->>Providers: Inference request<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP TLS 1.2+<br/>API key / IAM credentials
    Providers-->>OGXPod: Inference response
    OGXPod-->>Ingress: Response
    Ingress-->>Client: Response

    Note over Operator, K8sAPI: Flow 3: Legacy Adoption Migration
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Read LlamaStackDistribution<br/>Deployments
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Scale legacy Deployment to 0
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Transfer PVC ownership<br/>(remove legacy ownerRef,<br/>add labels, NO new ownerRef)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Update Service selectors<br/>to route to new OGXServer pods
